Sentencas: Cathode-electrolyte structures, for solid oxide fuel cells, are prepared by deposition of porous (LaSr)COO3 film on the surface of dense nanocrystalline 3 mol% Y2O3 stabilized zirconia electrolyte.
Titulo: Strontium-doped LaCoO3 perovskites in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The perovskite powder is prepared by a wet-chemical synthesis technique using metal-nitrates, mixed with a resin and organic solvents to form a paste that is deposited as a thick film by screen-printing technique.
Titulo: Strontium-doped LaCoO3 perovskites in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The characteristics of the synthesized powders, sintered samples and cathode-electrolyte structures are investigated..
Titulo: Strontium-doped LaCoO3 perovskites in solid oxide fuel cells
